createTable.remarks: Represents an emissions monitoring plan object

column.name: id
column.remarks: The emissions monitoring plan id (primary key)

column.name: account_id
column.remarks: The account id for which the emissions monitoring plan has been issued

column.name: data
column.remarks: emissions monitoring plan representation as json

column.name: file_document_uuid
column.remarks: The emissions monitoring plan's file document uuid
